This paper deals with natural language processing and argument analysis, which are typically covered in the arXiv CS sub-categories of computational linguistics (cs.CL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also involves semantic analysis and knowledge representation, which are relevant to information retrieval (cs.IR) and cybernetics (cs.CY).
